vote.title: Authorize a cooperative purchasing agreement for a boards and commissions solution, and a GovQA Public Records Request Management Software with Carahsoft Technology Corporation through the Department of Information Resources cooperative agreement, which is necessary to comply with the Freedom of Information Act for the period October 1, 2025 through December 31, 2026 - Not to exceed $244,941.97 - Financing: General Fund
